Nemanja Stankovic - Points

Nemanja Stankovic scores a career high 14 points (2016)

On September 23, 2016, Nemanja Stankovic set his career high in points in a France - NM1 game. That day he scored 14 points in Gries's road loss against Union T-L, 89-86. He also had 5 rebounds. He shot 1/2 from two, 4/8 from three, shooting at 50.0% from the field.

Nemanja Stankovic - Rebounds

Nemanja Stankovic grabs a career high 6 rebounds (2010)

On December 11, 2010, Nemanja Stankovic set his career high in rebounds in a Serbia - KLS game. That day he grabbed 6 rebounds in Superfund's road loss against Napredak, 77-72. He also had 13 points, 1 assist, 1 steal.

Nemanja Stankovic - Assists

Nemanja Stankovic gives a career high 3 assists (2010)

On December 18, 2010, Nemanja Stankovic set his career high in assists in a Serbia - KLS game. That day he dished 3 assists in Superfund's home loss against Vojvodina, 76-83. He also had 1 point, 1 rebound, 1 steal.

Nemanja Stankovic has a career high 4 steals (2016)

Nemanja Stankovic - Blocks

Nemanja Stankovic blocks a career high 1 shot (2007)

On November 17, 2007, Nemanja Stankovic tied his career high in blocks in a NCAA game. That day he went for 1 block in Chicago State Cougars's home win against Binghamton Bearcats, 81-60. He also had 2 points, 3 rebounds.

Nemanja Stankovic - Efficiency

Nemanja Stankovic records a career high 11 efficiency rating (2010)
